Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.25,0:01:13.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上菜了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:13.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Order up, Squidward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:16.63,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(880,444)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.63,0:01:17.76,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(760,490)}别问我今天过得怎样
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.20,0:01:26.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你刚看到我了没
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.20,0:01:26.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, did you see me?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.85,0:01:30.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就等会见  章鱼同事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.85,0:01:30.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, see you later, Squidinater
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:44.04,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(296,320)}此处点餐
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.36,0:01:33.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.36,0:01:33.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.07,0:01:37.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么  你准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:37.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, are you ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.28,0:01:38.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好回家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.28,0:01:38.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To go home?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.87,0:01:43.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错  是准备好为员工情谊日交换礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.87,0:01:43.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, to exchange gifts for employee brotherhood day
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.04,0:01:46.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  虽然你可以付工钱雇我收银
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:46.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, you pay me to stand behind this register
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.41,0:01:48.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后接单然后找零钱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.41,0:01:48.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and take orders and give change
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.36,0:01:50.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但就算你给的工钱再多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.36,0:01:50.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you could never pay me enough
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.34,0:01:51.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都不可能让我情深意重对待
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.34,0:01:51.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to act brotherly toward
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.34,0:01:53.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.34,0:01:53.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that guy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.18,0:02:00.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正因为你这种态度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:02:00.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That attitude of yours
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.70,0:02:03.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才要使出这种小把戏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.70,0:02:03.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is precisely why we're having this little shenanigan
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.02,0:02:04.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,注意好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:04.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, pay attention
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.95,0:02:07.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那小子有个惊喜要送你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.95,0:02:07.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The lad's got a surprise for you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.02,0:02:09.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  为了敬重我们的员工情谊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:09.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, in honor of employee brotherhood
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.73,0:02:11.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要送你一份礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:11.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I present to you a gift
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.59,0:02:12.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哒哒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.59,0:02:12.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ta-dah
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.83,0:02:14.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.83,0:02:14.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"I heart you"
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.75,0:02:16.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,试穿下吧  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:16.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Try it on, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.31,0:02:19.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上面画满了你的脸  一看就是给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.31,0:02:19.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's got you written all over it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.20,0:02:22.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不太确定要留多大的洞塞头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:22.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wasn't sure how big to make the hole for the head
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.45,0:02:24.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我就用西瓜来试尺寸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.45,0:02:24.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I used a watermelon for size
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.00,0:02:27.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:27.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you love it?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.29,0:02:30.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有点痒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:30.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a little itchy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.19,0:02:31.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这用什么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.19,0:02:31.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this thing made of?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.83,0:02:33.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,眼睫毛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:33.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eyelashes
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.09,0:02:39.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我可以继续干活拿最低工资了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.09,0:02:39.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, may I resume my minimum-wage duties?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.55,0:02:42.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先送出你的情谊礼物再说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:42.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,After you present your brotherhood gift
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.64,0:02:45.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会给那白痴买颗口香糖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.64,0:02:45.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll buy the little twerp a gumball
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.47,0:02:47.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行不行不行  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:47.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, no, no, lad
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.18,0:02:48.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可是知道规矩的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:48.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you know the rules
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.49,0:02:50.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,礼物必须自己做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.49,0:02:50.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you have to make the gift
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.14,0:02:53.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我唯一想要做的就是出门
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:53.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The only thing I'm making is for the exit
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.73,0:02:55.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样好点了没  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:55.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is this any better, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.36,0:02:59.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我用泪水做的这件毛衣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.36,0:02:59.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I made this one with my tears
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.57,0:03:04.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就知道你会改变主意  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:04.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd come around, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.88,0:03:06.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做个好礼物出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.88,0:03:06.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make something nice
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.12,0:03:10.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛不能给那小怪胎随便买样礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:10.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why can't I just buy something for the little weirdo?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.39,0:03:12.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,使劲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:12.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Heave ho
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.29,0:03:15.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是把我财宝搞掉下来一块
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:15.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you drop one single slice of me booty
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.34,0:03:16.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:16.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll have
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.50,0:03:17.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,割你们屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:17.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your booty
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.22,0:03:19.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:19.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, there
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.13,0:03:23.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那些家常手工派看起来挺好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:23.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those homemade pies sure look good
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.89,0:03:24.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是家常手工的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.89,0:03:24.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These aren't homemade
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.97,0:03:26.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是工厂制造的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:26.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They were made in a factory
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.81,0:03:28.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,炸弹工厂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:28.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a bomb factory
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.85,0:03:29.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些是炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:29.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're bombs
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.64,0:03:31.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:31.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that's too bad
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.64,0:03:34.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还以为那些是派  本来还想买的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:34.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought they were pies and I wanted to buy one
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.59,0:03:35.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,且慢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.59,0:03:35.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.07,0:03:39.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们刚刚说的炸弹都是玩笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:39.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We were just kidding about all that bomb stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.07,0:03:42.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,付二十五块钱就能买了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:42.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That'll be 25 bucks, please
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.23,0:03:43.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说这什么味的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.23,0:03:43.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, what flavor is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.95,0:03:44.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,樱桃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:44.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cherry
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.45,0:03:44.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,苹果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:44.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Apple
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.82,0:03:45.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,山莓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:45.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Raspberry
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.71,0:03:48.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能让那个蟹老头别烦我就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:48.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if it gets old man Krabs off my back
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.20,0:03:51.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,礼物做好了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:51.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, here it is, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.71,0:03:52.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新鲜出炉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:52.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,fresh from the oven
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.42,0:03:55.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我要回归正常生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:55.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be returning to my life now
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.33,0:03:57.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:57.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not yet
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.02,0:03:58.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得确定下你礼物做得行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:03:58.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to make sure you did it right
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.01,0:04:01.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:01.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a second
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.80,0:04:04.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,配牛奶更好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:04.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This would go great with some milk
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:08.31,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(882,642)}牛奶
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.98,0:04:13.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来你想杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:13.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, you tried to kill me
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.76,0:04:16.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好改旗易帜是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.76,0:04:16.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,over a little New-Age management, eh?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.06,0:04:18.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是蟹老板  我不知道会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:18.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But Mr. Krabs, I had no idea
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.27,0:04:19.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能解释清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:19.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can explain
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.62,0:04:21.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:21.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, are you okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.28,0:04:21.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听到有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:21.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I heard a
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.78,0:04:25.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有派
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:25.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A pie
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.95,0:04:27.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是章鱼哥送的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:27.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's from Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.55,0:04:28.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝收
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.55,0:04:28.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"To SpongeBob
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:30.91,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(774,286)}章鱼哥送\N海绵宝宝收
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:30.91,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(840,730)}你爱拿就拿吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.91,0:04:30.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你爱拿就拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:30.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, here you go"
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.91,0:04:32.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,经过就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:32.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And that's what happened
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.59,0:04:34.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二十五块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:34.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,25 dollars?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.43,0:04:35.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.43,0:04:35.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A bomb?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.68,0:04:37.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还在蟹堡王里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.68,0:04:37.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In the Krusty Krab?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.59,0:04:40.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚把它放这了的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.59,0:04:40.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's where you left it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.00,0:04:40.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:40.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not there
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.80,0:04:41.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:41.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.47,0:04:46.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你送的派  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:46.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the pie, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.81,0:04:52.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还非得杀了他不可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:52.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You had to kill him
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.81,0:04:55.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那小子用泪水给你哭出了件毛衣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:55.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The boy cries you a sweater of tears
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.90,0:04:56.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你却要杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:56.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you kill him
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.19,0:04:58.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么有脸心安理得活下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:04:58.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How are you going to live with yourself?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.77,0:04:59.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:04:59.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kill him?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.61,0:05:01.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的餐来了  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:01.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's your order, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.94,0:05:02.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:02.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.41,0:05:08.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  要怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:08.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no, no, what we got
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.45,0:05:09.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得给医院打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:09.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we got to call the hospital
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.33,0:05:10.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:10.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Won't do any good
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.47,0:05:11.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我先前就见过这种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:11.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've seen this before
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.92,0:05:13.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等到那派登上了本垒板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.92,0:05:13.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When that pie goes up to bat
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.02,0:05:15.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  等到抵达他下肠道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:15.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, hit his lower intestine
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.54,0:05:18.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你先前就见过了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:18.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've seen this before?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.81,0:05:20.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实见了有十一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:20.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,11 times, as a matter of fact
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.92,0:05:23.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂  医生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:23.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, hello, doctor?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.09,0:05:23.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,医院吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:23.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hospital?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.17,0:05:25.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:25.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It won't do any good?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.20,0:05:26.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,十一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:26.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eleven times?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.26,0:05:28.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:28.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's a goner
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.74,0:05:30.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得怎样交代人家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:30.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How do we tell him?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.10,0:05:31.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要交代
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:31.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't tell him
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.44,0:05:33.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说了只会让人家更难受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.44,0:05:33.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that'll only make him feel worse
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.47,0:05:36.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,依我看  他只能活到日落时分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:36.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The way I see it, he's only got till sunset
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.14,0:05:39.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为何要毁掉他活在世上的最后一天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:39.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why ruin his last day on earth?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.95,0:05:43.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那小子理应享受他最后的光阴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.95,0:05:43.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The lad deserves to enjoy his final hours
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.99,0:05:51.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说得对  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:51.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.08,0:05:56.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要让海绵宝宝最后的光阴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:56.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l'm going to make SpongeBob's final hours
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.83,0:05:58.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成为他最美好的光阴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:58.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the best he's ever had
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.69,0:06:01.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这回  我要投入爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:01.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And this time, there's going to be love
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.89,0:06:04.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多到能淹死他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:04.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so much he's going to drown in it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.88,0:06:08.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,淹死他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:08.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Drown in it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.97,0:06:12.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,写给自己  小心章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:12.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Note to self: Watch out for Squidward"
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.64,0:06:17.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:17.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.15,0:06:18.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.15,0:06:18.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.55,0:06:20.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我忘了跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.55,0:06:20.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I forgot to tell you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.10,0:06:22.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你礼物还有第二部分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:22.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there's a part two to your gift
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.52,0:06:24.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第二部分吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:24.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Part two"?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.05,0:06:25.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第二部分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:25.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Part two
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.24,0:06:27.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别给我这样干
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:27.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please don't do that
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.45,0:06:28.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第二部分要干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:28.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's for part two?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.58,0:06:32.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能想到什么最快乐的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:32.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, what's the most fun thing you can think of?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.62,0:06:34.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实我记了张清单
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:34.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually, I keep a list
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.29,0:06:36.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面列了我所有爱做的快乐事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:36.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of the most fun things I like to do
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.30,0:06:38.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我管这单子叫  情谊单
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:38.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I call it my "friendship list"
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.79,0:06:39.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:39.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.33,0:06:41.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我瞧一瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:41.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me see it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.35,0:06:43.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,更快乐的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:43.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The things that are extra fun
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.21,0:06:44.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都标成红色了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:44.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've written in red
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.17,0:06:47.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都是红色的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:47.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything's in red
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.11,0:06:48.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:48.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.73,0:06:51.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想完事最好现在就开始干
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.73,0:06:51.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'd better start now if want to get through this list
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.43,0:06:52.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免得你死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:52.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before you die
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.93,0:06:54.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,思来想去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:54.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of anticipation
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.50,0:06:56.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就开整吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:56.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then let's roll
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.68,0:06:58.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:58.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:01.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(674,768)}招聘
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.06,0:07:02.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看下  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:02.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Heads up, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.23,0:07:03.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好像要被换掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:03.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,looks like they're going to replace you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.27,0:07:04.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:04.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.40,0:07:07.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看下单子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:07.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now let's have a look at that list
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.86,0:07:10.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想做的第一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:10.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, the first thing I want to do
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.28,0:07:12.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是把我最好的朋友章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:12.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is show my best friend, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.95,0:07:15.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,介绍给全镇人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:15.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to everybody in town
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.87,0:07:18.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  这是我最好的朋友章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:18.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi there, this is my best friend, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.62,0:07:21.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小朋友们  快来看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:21.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, kids, check it out
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.70,0:07:24.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我最好的朋友章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.70,0:07:24.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is my best friend, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.54,0:07:27.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  我想向你介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:27.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, I want to show you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.46,0:07:29.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我最好的朋友章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:29.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my best friend, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.80,0:07:30.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,法兰克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:30.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Frank
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.59,0:07:32.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真高兴介绍完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:32.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Glad that's over
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.84,0:07:35.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好  因为我们要干下一件事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:35.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good, 'cause we're on to our next activity
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.55,0:07:36.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这件事是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:36.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Which is?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.55,0:07:38.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要把我最好的朋友章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.55,0:07:38.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to show my best friend, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.89,0:07:42.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,介绍给全镇人  但要先穿上鲑鱼装
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:42.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to everyone in town wearing a salmon suit
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.34,0:07:44.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你居然要穿鲑鱼装
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.34,0:07:44.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're going to be wearing a salmon suit?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.82,0:07:47.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真好笑  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:47.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a good one, Squidward
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:51.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz21.16\pos(1148,554)}介绍穿鲑鱼装的
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.99,0:07:51.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:51.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.11,0:07:53.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,敲门笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:53.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Knock-knock jokes
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.67,0:07:55.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  有人敲门
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:55.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squid, knock-knock
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.53,0:07:56.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:56.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.66,0:07:58.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:07:58.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.16,0:08:03.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:03.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:04.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz16.14\pos(1118,632)}敲门笑话
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.54,0:08:08.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请注意  倒朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:08.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look out, everyone, friends in reverse
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:11.88,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1120,606)\frz18.8}假装倒车
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:17.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1172,656)\frz16.08}模仿猿猴
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.35,0:08:19.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,左转  再
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:19.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Turn left, and
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.46,0:08:20.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.46,0:08:20.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,stop
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.39,0:08:23.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下明白拿我当脸用会怎样了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:23.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See, that's what it would be like if you had me for a face
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.51,0:08:25.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我喘不过气了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:25.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't breathe
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:26.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz20.02\pos(1188,614)}交换脸
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.40,0:08:28.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你确定应该要这样子戳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:28.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you should be poking it like that?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.90,0:08:30.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也不看看这边谁是医生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:30.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's the doctor here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:32.49,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1188,604)\frz21.52}剖心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:33.74,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1260,698)\frz22.8}杂耍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:34.95,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz21.16\pos(1148,554)}介绍穿鲑鱼装的
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.95,0:08:36.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,单子上的最后一件事是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:36.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the last thing on the list is
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.37,0:08:38.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是还有肢解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:38.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,does it involve more dismemberment?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.78,0:08:41.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟章鱼哥一起看日落
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:41.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Watch the sunset with Squidward"
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.33,0:08:42.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,日落
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:42.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Sunset"?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.04,0:08:46.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,依我看  那小子只能活到日落时分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:46.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The way I see it, the lad's got until sunset
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.17,0:08:48.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,届时那炸弹会命中他的下肠道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:48.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before that bomb hits his lower intestine
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.50,0:08:50.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:50.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.71,0:08:52.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.71,0:08:52.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.34,0:08:54.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好  再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:54.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, see you later
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.38,0:08:56.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:56.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.41,0:08:59.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要日落  那就给你日落
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:59.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you want a sunset, you'll get a sunset
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.47,0:09:02.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水下日落
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:02.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Underwater sunsets
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.97,0:09:04.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真美啊  对吧章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.97,0:09:04.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sure are beautiful eh, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.99,0:09:05.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.99,0:09:05.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.95,0:09:06.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:06.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.98,0:09:09.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有我们三个可真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:09.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is great just the three of us
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.32,0:09:10.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你  我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:10.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you, me
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.69,0:09:12.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有你在我们中间修的这堵砖墙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:12.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and this brick wall you built between us
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.99,0:09:13.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:13.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.03,0:09:17.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看日落会想到碗装的水果
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:17.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sunsets remind me of bowls of fruit
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.51,0:09:19.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看日落会想到什么  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.51,0:09:19.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do they make you think of, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.41,0:09:22.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:22.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,explosions
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.04,0:09:24.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  贬值
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:24.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, erosion
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.29,0:09:29.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,假如我现在就会被炸死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:28.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, if I were to die right now
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:29.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in some sort of fiery explosion
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.71,0:09:31.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起因都是有位朋友粗心大意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:31.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,due to the carelessness of a friend
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.64,0:09:33.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那也倒没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.64,0:09:33.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,well, that would just be okay
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.26,0:09:40.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉好像有东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:40.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If feels like something
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.24,0:09:41.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,掉到我下肠道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:41.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just dropped into my lower intestine
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.10,0:09:43.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闻着好像樱桃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:43.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Smells like cherry
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.48,0:09:45.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或许是葡萄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:45.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or maybe grape
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.85,0:09:46.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是蓝莓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:46.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Blueberry?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.73,0:09:49.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,日落  终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:49.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here it is, the sunset
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.46,0:09:51.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我特别喜欢这时候倒计时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:51.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I always love to count it down
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.81,0:09:52.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,五
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.81,0:09:52.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Five
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.78,0:09:54.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你数剩下的  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:54.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You do the rest, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.11,0:09:56.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.11,0:09:56.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Four
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.57,0:09:57.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:57.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,three
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.86,0:09:59.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:09:59.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,t-two
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.45,0:10:02.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:02.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,one
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.62,0:10:05.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像数得太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:05.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess we started too early
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.33,0:10:06.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,重新数一遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:06.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's start again
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.67,0:10:09.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,五  四
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:09.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Five, four
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.96,0:10:11.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:11.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,three
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.21,0:10:14.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:14.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,two
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.60,0:10:16.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.60,0:10:16.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.26,0:10:21.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  至少我还能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:21.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, at least I was able
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.22,0:10:24.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让他最后的光阴有了意义
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:24.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to make his last few hours meaningful
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.27,0:10:28.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可真是大好人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:28.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am such a good person
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.53,0:10:36.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  瞧瞧这招
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:36.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward, check this out
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.49,0:10:43.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  都已经学过傻子胡言乱语了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:43.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, we already played "Babble Like an Idiot"
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.03,0:10:45.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么还好端端在这
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:45.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why are you still here?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.12,0:10:47.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,单子上的事情都做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:47.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Since we finished everything on the list
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.33,0:10:48.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我就想再列一份
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:48.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd made up a new one
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.79,0:10:51.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这本书的创意都已经想好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:51.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I already filled up this book with ideas
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:52.21,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(836,142)}永远好朋友
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.42,0:10:54.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到一月份应该就能写完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:54.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We should be able to finish by January
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.23,0:10:56.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,书先别管
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:56.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forget the book
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.44,0:10:58.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,之所以我花上一整天陪你一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.44,0:10:58.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I spent the whole day with you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.72,0:11:01.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做各种荒唐可笑的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:11:01.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,doing all kinds of ridiculous things
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.30,0:11:03.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是因为你本来应该要爆了才对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:03.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because you were supposed to explode
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.39,0:11:05.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要我暴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:05.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You want me to explode?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.51,0:11:06.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:06.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.22,0:11:08.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就一直在等你爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:08.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's what I've been waiting for
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.52,0:11:10.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好吧  我尽力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:10.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll try
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.11,0:11:14.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.11,0:11:14.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.50,0:11:16.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要吃完甜点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:16.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are going to finish your dessert
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.86,0:11:19.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保证你会爱上的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:19.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you are going to like it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.11,0:11:21.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在轮你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:21.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, it's your turn
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.95,0:11:24.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想说的不是暴怒的暴  你个呆头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:24.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant, you barnacle head
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.08,0:11:25.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,暴得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:25.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good one
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.91,0:11:29.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,个鬼  你应该爆炸成几百万块才对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:29.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, you're supposed to explode into a million pieces
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.87,0:11:31.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么应该要那样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:31.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why would I do that?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.29,0:11:34.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为你吃的那个派是炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:34.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because the pie you ate was a bomb
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.21,0:11:35.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么派
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:35.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What pie?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.25,0:11:37.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天一大早我放柜台上的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:37.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The one I left sitting on the counter this morning
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.63,0:11:39.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还找海盗付了二十五块买的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:39.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that I bought from pirates for 25 bucks
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.97,0:11:41.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都不知道是炸弹的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:41.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I didn't know was a bomb
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.22,0:11:43.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还被你吃掉了的  那个派
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:43.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you ate it, that pie
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.09,0:11:44.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:44.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pie?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.76,0:11:47.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是说这个派啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:47.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean this pie
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.81,0:11:52.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直放口袋里要跟你一起分着吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:52.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was saving it in my pocket for us to share
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.69,0:11:53.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:53.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's eat
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:56.94,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1080,586)}裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.37,0:12:08.70,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(273,347)}真假蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:10.45,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz20.13\pos(446,396)}导演
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:14.50,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:12.50,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz20.13\pos(264,496)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:14.50,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz20.13\pos(434,328)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:16.75,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz20.13\pos(300,308)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:16.75,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz20.13\pos(510,640)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:16.75,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.75,0:12:19.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊  蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:19.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ah, the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:19.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,286)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.39,0:12:22.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡之家  内有十分机密的秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.39,0:12:22.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,home of the Krabby Patty, with its top secret formula
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.80,0:12:26.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有足够勇敢足够聪明的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:24.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,known only to those brave enough
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:26.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and intelligent enough
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.26,0:12:29.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才能领略其中的奥妙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.26,0:12:29.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to comprehend its culinary complexity
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.47,0:12:30.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板快看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:30.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.77,0:12:33.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我做到了  我做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:33.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm doing it, l'm doing it
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.27,0:12:34.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别卖傻了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:34.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quit fooling around, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.52,0:12:35.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有客人在等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:35.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we've got customers
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:40.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(428,352)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.48,0:12:37.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但凡哪里有份秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:37.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But wherever there is a secret recipe
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.27,0:12:40.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总会有人想要去偷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:40.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there is someone who wants to steal it
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.91,0:12:48.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在再来最后一步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:48.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now for the final touch
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.49,0:12:50.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:50.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.95,0:12:54.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,伪装在手  秘方我有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:54.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With this disguise that formula is as good as mine
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.21,0:13:03.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是海绵宝宝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:03.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you SpongeBob SquarePants?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.34,0:13:06.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:06.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, yes
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.64,0:13:08.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在下正是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:08.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,yes, I am
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.15,0:13:11.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你刚刚赢得了一百万块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.15,0:13:11.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then you've just won $1 million
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.81,0:13:15.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要回答我一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:15.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just have to answer one question
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.73,0:13:19.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡的秘密配方是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.73,0:13:19.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is the Krabby Patty secret formula?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.77,0:13:20.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:20.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.28,0:13:21.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:21.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.03,0:13:23.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:23.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.16,0:13:25.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡的秘密配方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.16,0:13:25.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krabby patty formula
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.20,0:13:26.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为蟹堡王之私有财产
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:26.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is the sole property of the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.49,0:13:29.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,部分或整体仅能与发明者蟹老板讨论
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:28.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and is only to be discussed, in part or in whole
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:29.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with its creator Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.12,0:13:30.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,擅自复制秘方将会受法律处罚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:30.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Duplication of this formula is punishable by law
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.87,0:13:32.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,处罚力度视程度而定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.87,0:13:32.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Restrictions apply, results may vary
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.13,0:13:39.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:39.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.75,0:13:43.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我把秘方说出来  不然有你好受的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:43.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'd better cough up that secret formula or else
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.13,0:13:44.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.13,0:13:44.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.27,0:13:45.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:45.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.42,0:13:46.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:46.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.97,0:13:48.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:48.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.36,0:13:49.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:49.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.97,0:13:54.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不可以对我这样做  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:54.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't do this to me, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.52,0:13:59.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我上过大学的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:13:59.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I went to college
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:00.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(436,664)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.98,0:14:03.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板那畜生可精明了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:03.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That Plankton is a clever beast
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.15,0:14:05.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你最好要密切注意好他  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:05.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got to keep a sharp eye out for him, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.94,0:14:08.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡法必须要严格实行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.94,0:14:08.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krabby Patty law must be enforced
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.95,0:14:11.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王的未来全都靠在那上面了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:11.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The future of the Krusty Krab depends on it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.95,0:14:13.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你放心  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:13.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.32,0:14:15.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要我这裤子还是方的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.32,0:14:15.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As long as these pants are square
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.61,0:14:17.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这海绵还是宝宝的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.61,0:14:17.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and this sponge is bob
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:21.54,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(846,920)}放 你 下 来
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.37,0:14:21.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我绝对不会让你失望的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:21.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I will not let you down
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.34,0:14:23.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:23.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.55,0:14:24.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能放我下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:24.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,could you let me down?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:28.72,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(450,492)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.80,0:14:28.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老天啊  这些蟹黄堡可真是好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:28.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Man, these patties sure are delicious
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.72,0:14:31.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道这秘方里面加了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:31.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's in that secret formula?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.26,0:14:33.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,十二号警报
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:33.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Code 12
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.72,0:14:39.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这回的伪装可骗不到我  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:39.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your disguises can't fool me this time, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.11,0:14:44.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,头部增强诊所的所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:44.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone at the Head Enhancement Clinic
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.73,0:14:46.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明明说过没人会注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:46.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,said nobody would notice
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.74,0:14:49.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:49.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.66,0:14:51.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你把我钱给吓跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:51.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're scaring away me money
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.24,0:14:52.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:52.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.49,0:14:54.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是尽了力在保护秘密配方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:54.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm just trying to protect the secret formula
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.80,0:14:57.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就算那样也不能乱扒别人脑袋  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.80,0:14:57.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's no reason to rip people's heads off, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.89,0:15:00.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要记好最重要的规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:15:00.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just remember the most important rule
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.00,0:15:01.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不提供免费纸巾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:01.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No free napkins?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.29,0:15:02.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:02.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.08,0:15:04.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,另外一条最重要的规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:04.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The other most important rule
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.38,0:15:05.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,讲秘方的那条
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:05.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,regarding the secret formula
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.71,0:15:08.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只能跟蟹老板讨论秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:08.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only discuss the secret recipe with Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.59,0:15:11.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要你这办妥了  秘方就安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:11.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As long as you do that, the secret is safe
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.89,0:15:14.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还一直以为最重要的规矩就是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:14.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l always thought the most important rule was
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.14,0:15:17.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能拖到明天  干嘛今天做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:17.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Why do today what you can put off till tomorrow?"
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.94,0:15:23.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天个鬼  不是昨天的明天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:23.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is today but yesterday's tomorrow?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.82,0:15:28.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天我要让你清查这边的所有东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:27.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Today, I want you to take inventory
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.65,0:15:28.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on everything in here
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.87,0:15:32.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每块腌椰菜每块肉饼都得记下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:32.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,every last pickle and patty must be accounted for
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.03,0:15:33.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命船长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:33.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.16,0:15:38.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两箱面包
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:38.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two boxes of buns
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.70,0:15:40.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三磅肉饼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:40.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Three pounds of patties
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.46,0:15:42.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:42.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.54,0:15:44.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又怎么了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:44.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What now, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.46,0:15:46.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  我就是蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:46.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right, I am Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.13,0:15:49.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的老板  你的统治者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:49.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your boss, your ruler
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.46,0:15:51.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.46,0:15:51.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your master
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.18,0:15:57.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可不是蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:57.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.77,0:16:01.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不让你今天剩下时间休假吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:16:01.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you take the rest of the day off?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.50,0:16:02.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.50,0:16:02.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.02,0:16:05.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就听你的了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:05.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,whatever you say, "Mr. Krabs"
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.90,0:16:09.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:09.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.61,0:16:11.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,控制易如反掌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:11.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sweet domination
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.40,0:16:13.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就对了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:13.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.82,0:16:15.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还没有痞老板的踪迹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:15.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No sign of Plankton yet
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.28,0:16:16.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老天爷啊  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:16.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gosh, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.58,0:16:17.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好像不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.58,0:16:17.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you don't look so good
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.99,0:16:20.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:20.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're so cold
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.83,0:16:23.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那只是我的铁布衫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:23.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's just my metal suit
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.85,0:16:25.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用来保护秘方的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:25.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I made it to protect the formula
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.99,0:16:28.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.99,0:16:28.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.25,0:16:30.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是呆头老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:30.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's that thick-headed Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.38,0:16:32.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他会坏了我的好事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:32.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He'll ruin everything
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.23,0:16:34.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看  有只水母
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.23,0:16:34.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, a jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.25,0:16:35.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来捉  我来捉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.25,0:16:35.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got it, I got it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:36.76,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(594,408)}中止
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.18,0:16:42.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来捉  我来捉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:42.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got it, I got it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.58,0:16:43.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.58,0:16:43.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.52,0:16:49.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  你铁布裤怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:49.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. Krabs, what happened to your metal pants?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.65,0:16:51.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别给我弄什么怪异行为  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:51.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't go all loopy on me, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.91,0:16:52.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要你来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.91,0:16:52.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need your help
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.11,0:16:54.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥到底跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:54.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And where in the high seas is Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.86,0:16:56.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你让他休假了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:56.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You gave him the day off
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.12,0:16:58.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,休
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:16:58.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Day
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.91,0:17:02.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,假
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:02.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Off
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.75,0:17:05.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都不知道这俩奇葩的字是几个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:05.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know the meaning of them horrible words
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.46,0:17:07.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别给我躺平了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:07.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now quit your laying around, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.17,0:17:08.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,垃圾都拿出去倒掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:08.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and take out that garbage
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.66,0:17:10.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都快害我起疹子了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.66,0:17:10.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's starting to give me a rash
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.05,0:17:11.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  蟹老板大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:11.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir, Mr. Krabs, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.47,0:17:16.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  只是要出去倒垃圾而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:16.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. Krabs, just taking out that garbage
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.82,0:17:18.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用管垃圾了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.82,0:17:18.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never mind that
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.14,0:17:19.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我需要跟你谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:19.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need to talk to you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.27,0:17:24.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:24.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.64,0:17:26.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都不知道你还长了放热电光眼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:26.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,l didn't know you had heat vision
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.73,0:17:29.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你管不着  我需要你告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:29.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never mind, I need you to tell me
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.23,0:17:30.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:30.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.15,0:17:32.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:32.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.53,0:17:34.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我付你工钱不是来雇你偷懒的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:34.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not paying you to stand around
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.84,0:17:36.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快回厨房里去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:36.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get back to the kitchen
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.17,0:17:37.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我还以为你要问我问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:37.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I thought you wanted to ask me a question
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.03,0:17:39.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实要问
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.03,0:17:39.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.00,0:17:40.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么不再努力点工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:40.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,why aren't you working harder?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.20,0:17:43.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我搞不懂  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:43.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.29,0:17:45.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:45.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.67,0:17:51.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板老是进进出出的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:51.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll never get that formula with that pest, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.38,0:17:52.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我肯定就拿不到秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.38,0:17:52.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,popping in and out like that
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.55,0:17:54.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:54.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.73,0:17:57.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直就存着这玩意以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.73,0:17:57.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been saving this for a rainy day
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.28,0:17:59.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看起来像是普普通通的一分钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.28,0:17:59.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,lt looks like an ordinary penny
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.78,0:18:02.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为本来就是普普通通的一分钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.78,0:18:02.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because it is an ordinary penny
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.78,0:18:05.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那笨蛋老螃蟹可贪了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.78,0:18:05.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That fool Krabs is too greedy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.14,0:18:08.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝对不会忽略你  我的小可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:08.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to ignore you, my little pretty
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.90,0:18:19.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这声音  听着像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:19.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That sound, it sounds like
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.54,0:18:20.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叮当作响的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.54,0:18:20.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the pitter-patter of
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.16,0:18:22.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.16,0:18:22.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,money
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.74,0:18:25.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要跑哪去  美人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.74,0:18:25.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where you going, beautiful?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.50,0:18:26.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:26.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.75,0:18:28.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:28.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.96,0:18:30.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:30.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.17,0:18:33.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:33.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.38,0:18:39.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟秘方之间没有障碍了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.38,0:18:39.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing stands between me and that secret formula now
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.64,0:18:47.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,擦擦擦  我喜欢擦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:47.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Scrubba-dub-dub, l love to rub
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.48,0:18:50.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  擦个地板而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:50.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. Krabs, just doing a little scrubbing
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.15,0:18:52.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:52.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.56,0:18:54.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:54.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it is me, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.78,0:18:56.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:56.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the flesh
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.00,0:18:57.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就站在你面前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.00,0:18:57.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,standing right in front of you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.87,0:18:59.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,旁边没一个外人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.87,0:18:59.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with no one else around
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.07,0:19:00.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这我知道  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.07,0:19:00.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can see that, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.95,0:19:03.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得应该可以讨论蟹黄堡秘方了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.95,0:19:02.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought we might discuss
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:03.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Krabby Patty secret formula
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.99,0:19:05.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这不一话筒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:05.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a microphone?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.41,0:19:06.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:06.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.34,0:19:07.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还确实是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.34,0:19:07.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, yes, it is
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.58,0:19:09.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我必须得把这铁布衫给洗洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.58,0:19:09.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I must get this shirt cleaned
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.71,0:19:12.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  现在给我说秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:12.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, now tell me the secret formula
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.00,0:19:15.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是老板  还没做秘密握手式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:15.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, sir, we haven't done the secret handshake yet
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.00,0:19:16.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实  来握手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:16.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, here, let's shake
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.55,0:19:20.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,握手式不握手  忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:20.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We don't shake with our hands, remember?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.09,0:19:23.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  那你先来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.09,0:19:23.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right, why don't you start
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.26,0:19:24.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,单脚独立
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:24.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We stand on one foot
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.97,0:19:28.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿杯巧克力奶稳稳顶在头上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.97,0:19:28.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,balance a glass of chocolate milk on our heads
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.56,0:19:30.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,唱裤头村村歌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:30.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and sing the Bikini Bottom national anthem
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.20,0:19:32.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哦  裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.20,0:19:32.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.84,0:19:34.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们对你起誓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:34.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We pledge our hearts to you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.31,0:19:35.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,共忠实  共深沉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:35.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As faithful, as deep
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.61,0:19:37.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,共真诚  共蔚蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:37.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as true, as blue
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.28,0:19:39.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村我们爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:39.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bikini Bottom, we love you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.82,0:19:41.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该说秘方了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:41.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Formula time?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.17,0:19:42.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.17,0:19:42.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.57,0:19:44.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,六个半小时后
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.66,0:19:53.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吃  这意大利面真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:53.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yum, yum, this spaghetti sure is good
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.80,0:19:54.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打嗝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.80,0:19:54.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Belch
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.56,0:19:57.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肉丸肉丸  下面放着意大利面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:57.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Meatball, meatball, spaghetti underneath
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.40,0:20:00.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,方饺方饺  简直如同大堡礁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:20:00.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ravioli, ravioli, Great Barrier Reef
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.72,0:20:03.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  讲点秘方的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:03.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, now let's hear that formula
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.57,0:20:04.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.57,0:20:04.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.34,0:20:06.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还不行  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:06.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no can do, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.17,0:20:08.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.17,0:20:08.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wha-a-a-a-t?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.22,0:20:10.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可你说的都照办了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:10.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But we did everything you said
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.89,0:20:13.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有规矩我都遵守了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:13.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I followed all the rules
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.18,0:20:17.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还都用吸管吃了105颗甘草糖豆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.18,0:20:16.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I even ate 105 black licorice jelly beans
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:17.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,through a straw
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.61,0:20:19.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凭什么不能告诉我秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.61,0:20:19.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, why can't you tell me the formula?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.32,0:20:21.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你定的规矩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:21.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's your rule
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.53,0:20:23.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能把秘方给说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:23.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,never speak the formula
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.36,0:20:24.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你交代过我要把秘方装进
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:24.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You told me to keep it in
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.24,0:20:26.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个瓶子里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:26.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this bottle
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.33,0:20:28.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就对了  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:28.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is it, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.74,0:20:30.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,轻一点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:30.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gently, now
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.67,0:20:43.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒抽一口气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:43.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gasp
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.63,0:20:45.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么能这样  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:45.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How could you do this, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.94,0:20:48.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把我的秘方交给这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.94,0:20:48.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Giving me secret formula to this
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.12,0:20:49.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冒牌货
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.12,0:20:49.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,impostor?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.56,0:20:51.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要听他话  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:51.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't listen to him, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.90,0:20:52.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:52.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remember
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.81,0:20:56.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,方饺方饺  快给我送秘方来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.81,0:20:56.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ravioli, ravioli, give me the formuoli
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.06,0:20:57.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  别
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:20:57.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, no
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.11,0:20:58.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别听他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.11,0:20:58.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,don't listen to him
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.30,0:21:00.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才是真正的蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.30,0:21:00.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the real Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.28,0:21:03.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要听他的话  他明显是个机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.28,0:21:03.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't listen to him, he's obviously a robot
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.07,0:21:07.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要是个机器人  虽然本来就不是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.07,0:21:07.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if I was a robot, which I'm not
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.14,0:21:09.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至少我组装得特像模像样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:09.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,at least I'm well put together
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.03,0:21:11.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不像是某些蒸汽发动的生锈废铁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.03,0:21:11.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not some rusted-out, steam-driven pile of junk
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.42,0:21:13.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说谁是蒸汽发动的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.42,0:21:13.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who you calling "steam-driven"?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.16,0:21:14.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肃静
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.16,0:21:14.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quiet
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.10,0:21:20.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等我知道谁才是真蟹老板才可以动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:20.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Until I know who the real Mr. Krabs is, nobody moves
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.46,0:21:22.67,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1004,696)}塔塔酱
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.92,0:21:22.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在此之前没人会受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.92,0:21:22.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,nobody gets hurt
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.92,0:21:24.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,塔塔酱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:24.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tartar sauce?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.38,0:21:25.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,悠着点使那玩意  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:25.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take it easy with that thing, son
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.93,0:21:29.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才有话语权
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:29.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll do the talking around here
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.93,0:21:32.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要向你们两个问一点问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.93,0:21:32.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I'll just ask you two a couple of questions
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.15,0:21:37.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有真正的蟹老板才答得上来的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.15,0:21:37.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,questions only the real Mr. Krabs could answer
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.56,0:21:38.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.56,0:21:38.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, then
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.90,0:21:43.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一题  蟹堡王几点几分开门
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:43.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First question: What time does the Krusty Krab open?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.05,0:21:44.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上午九点半
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.05,0:21:44.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,9:30 a.m.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.36,0:21:44.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,答对了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.36,0:21:44.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.95,0:21:47.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一招就中了  假老板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.95,0:21:47.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's one strike, "Mr. Fake"
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.22,0:21:47.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.22,0:21:47.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.45,0:21:51.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,答题竞赛归我管  问题归我问
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.45,0:21:51.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm running this quiz show, I'll ask the questions
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.79,0:21:54.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有我才能够说但是俩字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.79,0:21:54.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,lf there's going to be any "buts," they're going to be from me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.75,0:21:56.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的  第二题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.75,0:21:56.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, question number two
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.09,0:21:58.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡一个多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.09,0:21:58.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How much does a Krabby Patty cost?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.06,0:21:59.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两块九毛九
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.06,0:21:59.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,$2.99
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.46,0:22:01.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要星期三的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.46,0:22:01.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On Wednesday
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.25,0:22:03.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,九毛九
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.25,0:22:03.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,99 cents
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.56,0:22:04.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又答对了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.56,0:22:04.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right again
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.62,0:22:06.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你现在越看越假了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.62,0:22:06.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're starting to look pretty phony right about now
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.80,0:22:08.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要是你的话就特别紧张了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.80,0:22:08.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd be nervous if I were you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.76,0:22:12.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有真真正正的蟹老板能答上来这题
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.76,0:22:12.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, only the really real Mr. Krabs can answer this
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.31,0:22:16.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果在一月第三个周三讨论秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.31,0:22:14.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If we're discussing the secret formula
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.98,0:22:16.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on the third Wednesday in January
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.48,0:22:18.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且吃过香草布丁之后外面没下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.48,0:22:17.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and it's not raining outside
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.48,0:22:18.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,after we gargle with vanilla pudding
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.88,0:22:19.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.88,0:22:19.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what do we do?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.45,0:22:20.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这道题简单
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.45,0:22:20.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's an easy one
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.54,0:22:21.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:21.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.02,0:22:21.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.02,0:22:21.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.44,0:22:22.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想想  如果是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.44,0:22:22.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see, if it's a
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.52,0:22:23.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果是一月  吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.52,0:22:23.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If it's January with
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.98,0:22:25.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃了香草布丁  你会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.98,0:22:25.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with vanilla pudding, you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.74,0:22:28.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.74,0:22:28.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pass
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.11,0:22:30.37,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,376)}特餐
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.99,0:22:30.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.99,0:22:30.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.91,0:22:32.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.91,0:22:32.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.16,0:22:33.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再给我个机会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.16,0:22:33.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me another chance
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.97,0:22:35.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,永别了  冒牌蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.97,0:22:35.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So long, Imitation Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.99,0:22:36.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.99,0:22:36.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.25,0:22:39.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就知道真货一直都是你  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.25,0:22:39.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew it was you all along, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.21,0:22:40.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.21,0:22:40.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.30,0:22:41.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你了  上当宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.30,0:22:41.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Sponge-Dupe
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.72,0:22:48.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的好运硬币可别忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.72,0:22:48.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't forget your lucky penny
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.63,0:22:51.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(898,668)}自爆
Dialogue: 1,0:22:52.55,0:22:54.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天肯定是你的幸运日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.55,0:22:54.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This must be your lucky day
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.97,0:22:58.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自爆投币口已激活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.97,0:22:58.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The self-destruct coin slot has been activated
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.87,0:23:00.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,十秒后起爆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.87,0:23:00.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ten seconds till detonation
Dialogue: 1,0:23:01.48,0:23:03.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,投币自爆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.48,0:23:03.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Coin-operated self-destruct"?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:03.87,0:23:05.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这想法可不太妙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.87,0:23:05.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not one of my better ideas
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.83,0:23:08.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.83,0:23:08.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:23:14.99,0:23:17.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果说那是痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.99,0:23:17.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If that was Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:23:18.50,0:23:19.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:19.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:23:20.25,0:23:21.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.25,0:23:21.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:23:22.00,0:23:23.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.00,0:23:23.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yum, yum
Dialogue: 1,0:23:23.24,0:23:25.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,伸回去  你这大饿手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.24,0:23:25.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Back, you hungry hand, back
Dialogue: 1,0:23:25.35,0:23:26.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.35,0:23:26.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:23:28.38,0:23:30.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.38,0:23:30.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, Mr. Krabs, I'm sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:23:30.69,0:23:32.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还以为你是个冒牌货
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.69,0:23:32.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought you were a phony
Dialogue: 1,0:23:33.05,0:23:34.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没关系的  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.05,0:23:34.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's okay, me lad
Dialogue: 1,0:23:34.41,0:23:36.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要秘方还能安全就行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.41,0:23:36.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Long as the secret formula's safe again
Dialogue: 1,0:23:36.53,0:23:39.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过  那分钱要从你工资里扣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.53,0:23:39.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,However, that penny's coming out of your paycheck
Dialogue: 1,0:23:44.23,0:23:45.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.23,0:23:45.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
